snippet.title: The Necrodemic Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The wait is finally over! The #Necrodemic Official Trailer is live!
First #freetoplay #nftgame  with over $25,000 rewards with play and earn features! 

Join #waitlist now at app.bullieverse.com!

Participate in the Waitlist with Gleam Competition to win $25,000 worth of Rewards)

➡️ Join - https://bit.ly/GleamYoutube

Note - Registering for Waitlist on app.bullieverse.com is free. You can create your account with email and connect your crypto e-wallet. No funds required to join the waitlist program. 

==================================
(For COBI #nft holders)

➡️ Create your account now: https://bit.ly/3ChXopw

➡️ Subscribe to our channel for the latest streams and videos: https://bit.ly/3fTU8ZR

==================================

** About Necrodemic **

Necrodemic, is a Free to Play survival-based thriller. Defeat zombie bears to earn essence. Essence can be used to purchase more powerful weapons, ammo, and perks that increase players' chances of survival. Rank in daily competitions and win loot box prizes and a daily leaderboard that rewards players!

==================================

About Bullieverse

Bullieverse is an Open Metaverse where NFTs come to life through an immersive gaming experience built on the Unreal engine. This ecosystem is rapidly expanding, with new players joining the community, and new games being created with in-game assets & fair incentives, aligned alongside Web3 ethos. Through Bullieverse DAO, Bullieverse will progressively decentralize to become a community-owned metaverse governed by the $Bull token holders.
